Medical Health App for Patients

Himanshu Sharma

Hello Friends,

This shot is a rebound of medical health dashboard. However, this has different features and functionalities. A patient can keep tabs on his medical/health history through this product. Patient can view/navigate different hospitals and vital statistics as well as doctors details and past treatment history.

You can also keep tabs on vital statistics of your body and view how it fluctuates over a period of time.

Like it to show your love.
